file.content: {"openapi":"3.0.3","info":{"title":"Session service","description":"HTTP service that showcase the use of HTTP cookies in Goa services.","version":"1.0"},"servers":[{"url":"http://localhost:80","description":"Default server for session"}],"paths":{"/":{"get":{"tags":["session"],"summary":"use_session session","operationId":"session#use_session","parameters":[{"name":"SID","in":"cookie","description":"Session ID","allowEmptyValue":true,"required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","description":"Session ID","example":"Mollitia aut quis."},"example":"At mollitia itaque facere voluptas."}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"OK response.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/CreateSessionResponseBody"},"example":{"message":"Omnis eligendi."}}}}}},"post":{"tags":["session"],"summary":"create_session session","operationId":"session#create_session","requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/CreateSessionRequestBody"},"example":{"name":"Ut quas sit at illum tempore ad."}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"OK response.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/CreateSessionResponseBody"},"example":{"message":"Aliquam aut iste incidunt impedit maiores."}}}}}}}},"components":{"schemas":{"CreateSessionRequestBody":{"type":"object","properties":{"name":{"type":"string","description":"Name of session","example":"Necessitatibus eum atque ut."}},"example":{"name":"Quis sunt sed culpa tempore natus est."},"required":["name"]},"CreateSessionResponseBody":{"type":"object","properties":{"message":{"type":"string","description":"User message","example":"Et dolor."}},"example":{"message":"Aliquid illum dolore quasi voluptates mollitia deserunt."},"required":["message"]}}},"tags":[{"name":"session","description":"The session service illustrates managing user sessions with cookies."}]}
